        <p>Miami has roughly 80 med spas competing for patient attention. Most are invisible on Google. The ones that rank are using professional SEO. If you're shopping for a <a href="/medspas/seo/">med spa SEO agency</a>, you're in the right place. This guide walks through 12 established firms, one local specialist, and breaks down what you're paying for.</p>

        <p>The med spa marketing space is fragmented. National agencies bring big teams and higher price tags. Local Miami agencies know your market. Boutique firms offer flexibility and hands-on delivery. None of these choices is wrong, but picking the wrong fit wastes money and time.</p>

        <p>We evaluated these agencies on three criteria: stated experience with med spas, public pricing or reliable estimates, and verifiable track record. This isn't a ranking. It's a transparent breakdown so you can make an informed choice.</p>

        <div class="key-takeaways">
