        <h2>How to Choose Between National and Local Miami Med Spa SEO</h2>

        <p>Choosing depends on three factors: budget, timeline, and what you're outsourcing.</p>

        <p><strong>Pick a national agency if:</strong> You have a budget over $2,000/mo, you want a large team supporting your account, you operate multiple med spas, you need full-service (design, content, ads, SEO), or you want written guarantees and established playbooks. Understand that you're trading personalization for scale.</p>

        <p><strong>Pick a local Miami agency if:</strong> Your budget is $500–$1,500/mo, you want direct access to the person doing your work, you're new to SEO and want education, you appreciate market-specific strategy, or you value flexibility over contract locks. Expect more agility and fewer layers of bureaucracy.</p>

        <p>There's no universal answer. A $5,000/mo national agency isn't better than a $700/mo local firm if the local firm is the right fit for your needs and your market.</p>

        <h2>What Med Spa SEO Actually Costs in 2026</h2>

        <p>SEO pricing breaks into four tiers. Basic SEO (Google Business Profile optimization, keyword research, on-page tuning) runs $400–$800/mo. Mid-tier (basic + monthly content, link building, technical SEO) costs $1,200–$2,000. Full-service (mid-tier + paid ads, conversion optimization, reporting) ranges $2,500–$5,000. Enterprise (multiple services, dedicated account management, custom reporting) exceeds $5,000/mo.</p>

        <p>Most med spas start in the mid-tier zone ($1,200–$2,000). This covers the essentials without expensive add-ons. Expect to see results in 4 to 8 weeks for quick wins like GBP optimization, and 3 to 6 months for meaningful ranking gains.</p>

        <p>Hidden costs exist. Some agencies charge setup fees ($500–$2,000). Others require ad spend minimums or take a percentage of your ad budget. Read contracts carefully for these.</p>

        <p>For a full pricing breakdown by service (SEO, GBP, ads, reputation) and recommendations by clinic stage, see our companion guide: <a href="/blog/med-spa-marketing-cost-miami/">med spa marketing costs in Miami</a>. To project ROI on a specific budget, use the <a href="/free-tools/med-spa-marketing-roi-calculator/">Miami Med Spa Marketing ROI Calculator</a>.</p>

